code: @Override public int selectChannel(SerializationDelegate<StreamRecord<T>> record) {     K key.     try {         key = keySelector.getKey(record.getInstance().getValue()).     } catch (Exception e) {         throw new RuntimeException("Could not extract key from " + record.getInstance().getValue(), e).     }     return KeyGroupRangeAssignment.assignKeyToParallelOperator(key, maxParallelism, numberOfChannels). }
@Override public void configure(int maxParallelism) {     KeyGroupRangeAssignment.checkParallelismPreconditions(maxParallelism).     this.maxParallelism = maxParallelism. }
